00:00:55.033 --> 00:00:58.166
who saw one of Isaac's films
in a Brooklyn bar one night

00:00:58.166 --> 00:01:00.600
and immediately got
on a plane to Uganda

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:02.266
to meet the genius behind it.

00:01:02.266 --> 00:01:06.533
He never left, eventually
becoming Isaac's co-producer.

00:01:06.533 --> 00:01:08.400
I think people are
coming for the same reason

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:09.800
